      <h3 class="title">Aki the Chosen - Vale of Eternal Blossoms (31.2, 74.2)</h3>
      <div class="story">
        <p>This where we like to start our day of pet leveling. What we tend to do is fly to the
          tamer as we fly, select the pet we will use on the this tamer. Then we get there we put
          on the food buffs for the pets. With this tamer the only fight that is of concern is
          Whiskers, only because this is where alot of swapping happens the other two are this easy.
          the Idol can take care of all the pets if you want. If this strat is not good for you there is a
          Wowhead link at the bottom, so you cant comb through the other strats.
        </p>
        <h4 class="title">The Pets</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Idol (1,1,1)</li>
            <li>Dread Hatchling (1,1,1)</li>
            <li>Carry</li>
            <p>The Dread hatchling can be any flying pet does not really matter. With our strat, on this boss,
              you can use a level one pet.
            </p>
            <p>After this fight one of the pets will be level 11 without a food buff</p>
          </ul>
        <h4 class="title">The Strat</h4>
        <br />
        <h6 class="title">Chirrup</h6>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Sandstorm</li>
            <li>Crush till you beat Chirrup</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <h6 class="title">StormLash</h6>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Deflect</li>
            <li>Crush till you beat StormLash</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <h6 class="title">Whiskers</h6>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Swap to the Carry pet Whiskers will just dive in move one</li>
            <li>Swap to flying pet</li>
            <li>Use Peck till the flyer dies or win</li>
            <li>Swap Idol and save Deflect to Whiskers dies</li>
            <li>Crush till you beat Whiskers</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
